title: Index
summary: Index might be a good recipe to expand your main course recipe box. For $5.14 per serving, this recipe covers 40% of your daily requirements of vitamins and minerals. This recipe serves 2. One serving contains 999 calories, 68g of protein, and 50g of fat. 1 person were glad they tried this recipe. A mixture of pasta, grilled corn and avocado pasta salad, honey sriracha coconut grilled chicken fingers, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so yummy. To use up the pasta you could follow this main course with the Chocolate Dessert Pasta as a dessert. It is brought to you by Iowa Girl Eats. From preparation to the plate, this recipe takes around 45 minutes. All things considered, we decided this recipe deserves a spoonacular score of 72%. This score is good.
